Private Dining + Special Events
BEAUTIFUL BANQUETS, EXCEPTIONAL EVENTS
Planning an event? Give your team room to breathe in our cool and colorful event space, complete with catering options and flexible set-ups. We are unrivaled when it comes to romantic wedding receptions, stellar banquets, corporate meetings, and specialty events. We can accommodate meetings and events for groups of two to 65 and we are equipped with all the latest technology to keep your meeting on point.
